#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.mf.flatmap.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.mf.flatmap"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.series_flatmap:1 of
msgid ""
"Apply the given function to each row and then flatten results. Use this "
"method if your transformation returns multiple rows for each input row."
msgstr ""
"对每一行应用给定函数，然后展平结果。如果您的转换对每个输入行返回多行，请"
"使用此方法。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.series_flatmap:4 of
msgid ""
"This function applies a transformation to each element of the Series, "
"where the transformation can return zero"
msgstr "此函数对 Series 的每个元素应用一个转换，该转换可以返回零个"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.series_flatmap:5 of
msgid ""
"or multiple values, effectively flattening Python generator, list-liked "
"collections and DataFrame."
msgstr "或多个值，从而有效地展平 Python 生成器、类列表集合和 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.series_flatmap of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.series_flatmap:7 of
msgid ""
"Function to apply to each element of the Series. It should accept a "
"scalar value (or an array if ``raw=True``) and return a list or iterable "
"of values."
msgstr ""
"应用于 Series 每个元素的函数。它应接受一个标量值（如果 ``raw=True`` 则为"
"数组）并返回一个值的列表或可迭代对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.series_flatmap:10 of
msgid "Specify dtypes of returned DataFrame. Can't work with dtype."
msgstr "指定返回的 DataFrame 的 dtypes。不能与 dtype 同时使用。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.series_flatmap:12 of
msgid "Specify dtype of returned Series. Can't work with dtypes."
msgstr "指定返回的 Series 的 dtype。不能与 dtypes 同时使用。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.series_flatmap:14 of
msgid "Specify name of the returned Series."
msgstr "指定返回的 Series 的名称。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.series_flatmap:16 of
msgid "Positional arguments to pass to ``func``."
msgstr "传递给 ``func`` 的位置参数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.series_flatmap:18 of
msgid "Additional keyword arguments to pass as keywords arguments to ``func``."
msgstr "作为关键字参数传递给 ``func`` 的额外关键字参数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.series_flatmap of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.series_flatmap:20 of
msgid "Result of DataFrame when dtypes specified, else Series."
msgstr "当指定 dtypes 时返回 DataFrame，否则返回 Series。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.series_flatmap of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.series_flatmap:24 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.series_flatmap:25 of
msgid ""
"The ``func`` must return an iterable of values for each input element. If"
" ``dtypes`` is specified, `flatmap` will return a DataFrame, if ``dtype``"
" and ``name`` is specified, a Series will be returned."
msgstr ""
"``func`` 必须为每个输入元素返回一个值的可迭代对象。如果指定了 ``dtypes``"
"，`flatmap` 将返回一个 DataFrame；如果指定了 ``dtype`` 和 ``name``，则将"
"返回一个 Series。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.series_flatmap:28 of
msgid ""
"The index of the resulting DataFrame/Series will be repeated based on the"
" number of output rows generated by ``func``."
msgstr "生成的 DataFrame/Series 的索引将根据 ``func`` 生成的输出行数重复。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.series_flatmap:32 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.series_flatmap:42 of
msgid "Define a function that takes a number and returns a list of two numbers:"
msgstr "定义一个函数，该函数接受一个数字并返回两个数字的列表："

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.series_flatmap:47 of
msgid ""
"Specify ``dtype`` with a function which returns list to return more "
"elements as a Series:"
msgstr "通过指定 ``dtype`` 和返回列表的函数，将更多元素作为 Series 返回："

#: maxframe.dataframe.extensions.flatmap.series_flatmap:58 of
msgid "Specify ``dtypes`` to return multi columns as a DataFrame:"
msgstr "指定 ``dtypes`` 以将多列作为 DataFrame 返回："

